{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Shiranui, the Do-It-All Shopkeeper\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2: Daily Life of a Shopkeeper<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Port - Supply Shop","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"On my day off, I decided to hide in the bushes next to the shop to see just what was going on.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Shiranui, did the package I asked you for arrive yet?","actor":303080,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"Not yet, but I will deliver it to you myself once I get it.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":301180},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"All right, thanks. As usual, keep it on the down low, okay?","actor":303080,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I know. Although sooner or later... no, someone surely has discovered your \"secret\" by now.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"You sure don't hold any punches with your straightforwardness... Oh well, I'm counting on you again.","actor":303080,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Mhm.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"... ...","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Shiranui, I see you're still holding down this shabby fort like always.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":301240},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"I see you're still running your mouth like always.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":301180},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"You're one to talk~","actor":301240,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"H-Hatsushimo, don't talk like that...","actor":301210,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"It's totally fine, Hatsuharu, getting into a spat is just the daily routine for these two.","actor":301230,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Don't make it sound like we get along...","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Having said all that, since you're already here, might as well come in and take a look.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"... ... ... ...","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Phew, after that... let me check on the status of Kuroshio's ninja equipment and Oyashio's doll supplies.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":301180},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"That's right, the new fabrics that Urakaze asked for should be here in about two days.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"...From an observer's standpoint, one has to admit that Shiranui is a pretty diligent shopkeeper.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"BUZHIHUO2","fadeOut":1.5}